<HEADLINE> Air Crash Occurs in Southern Mozambique </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MAPUTO, November 20 (Xinhua) -- Six people were killed and one
was injured when a Cessna-402 plane crashed in Vilanculo Bay in
the northern Mozambican province of Inhambane on Wednesday, the
Mozambique Information Agency reported today.
</P>
