Kye Moon led the preliminary stage with 642 points, followed by
countrymen Kim Bo Ram, 631 points, and Hong Sung Chil, 621 points.
</P>
<P>
In the men's team event, South Korea led with 1,894 points
followed by Japan with 1,794 and Chinese Taipei 1,777 points.
