up, while outstanding civil works on stadia would also commence.
</P>
<P>
Nigeria will guarantee that arrangement associated with entry
and exit permits, playing fields, transportation, customs service,
currency exchange services, hotel facilities and security meet
FIFA's high standards, the head of state said. 
