<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, November 21 (Xinhua) -- Russian President Boris Yeltsin
today pledged to enhance ties with Ukraine, saying that the people
of the two countries wish to see their countries getting closer.
</P>
<P>
"Today, Russian-Ukrainian relations are on the mend. Now the
main thing is that everyone feels the results," Yeltsin said in
his weekly nationwide radio address.
