established at a cost of 9.78 million US dollars. The company
will mainly use domestic raw materials, and most of its products
will be exported.
</P>
<P>
The Shanghai facility will supply bearings to FAG branches
overseas and Germany's Volkswagon, one of the world's major
automobile manufacturers, with projected 1998 exports expected to
hit 10 million US dollars.
</P>
<P>
An FAG representative said the company will increase
investments in the Shanghai branch on an annual basis through the
end of this century. 
