<HEADLINE> Share Prices Rally on Singapore Market </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SINGAPORE, November 21 (Xinhua) -- Share prices rallied on the
Singapore market as the benchmark Straits Times Industrials Index
gained 1.37 points to close at 1642.4 today.
</P>
<P>
