<HEADLINE> Beijing's Largest State Grocery Changes Governmental Identity </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, November 21 (Xinhua) -- Beijing's largest state-owned
grocery store is changing into a new company with a new strategy
using science and technology enhancement and chainstore methods,
even though it will continue to store food for the government.
</P>
