<TEXT>
<P>
DHAKA, November 21 (Xinhua) -- The Bangladeshi government has
embarked on a program of modernizing the entire telecommunications
sector in the country, sources from the Ministry of Post and
Telecommunications said here today.
</P>
<P>
This statement was made by Mohammad Nasim, Minister of Post and
Telecommunications while addressing a session of "technical
presentation" of the digital telephone switching system in
Bangladesh Thursday.
