<HEADLINE> African Justice Ministers to Meet in Addis </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ADDIS ABABA, November 20 (Xinhua) -- The first ever meeting of
African ministers of justice, human rights and attorneys-general
is to take place here on December 12-13, a press release from the
Organization of African Unity (OAU) said here today.
</P>
<P>
According to the press release, the ministerial session shall
be preceded by a meeting of legal experts from December 8 to 11.
</P>
<P>
