</P>
<P>
WASHINGTON -- President Bill Clinton, wary of Iraq's permission
to allow U.N. weapons inspectors including Americans back on their
work, said on Thursday that he will "wait and see" Iraqi President
Saddam Hussein's next action.
</P>
<P>
