<HEADLINE> European Shares Surge on Wall Street, Tokyo Rebound </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, November 20 (Xinhua) -- Leading stock markets in
Europe surged strongly Thursday and all ended sharply
higher, supported by Wall Street's rise and Tokyo's revival
as well as a steady dollar.
</P>
<P>
London's FTSE 100 index extended early gains as Wall
